result.name: Cóm Bánh Mì

reviews.text:
Decent food, comfy place.
Nice to have when you really miss Viet food.
Not the best value though.
Good value, genuine Vietnamese food done well.

As someone who’s spent time in Vietnam’s rural places - this place is both authentic and fantastic value. The Banh Mi is wonderfully on point (including the crunchy white baguette which is very rare in HK!); noodle salads are also great and fresh.

Nice place, nice food and nice price. Even though this Vietnamese restaurant does not offer so many dishes as other restaurant, she can focus on several main courses and snacks. So she can serve you the dishes with the best taste.

Apart from signle order, she also provides the combo set with the price HK$80-90, a main course, a snack and a drink.
In a corridor, a good value menu with starter such as papaya salad, a pho soup and a drink, quick service

result.name: Cóm Bánh Mì

reviews.text:
又到食Lunch時間，有時真係諗唔到食咩？打算落到樓，行到邊就食到邊，點知就比我發現到你了 - COM BANH MI。

店內以長方形設計，左面有一排面牆的位置，右面則有4人坐的餐位，地方唔算太大，但地方整潔；配合藍色牆身，掛著一系列美食相片，更顯平凡中帶點色彩。

還有openrice 外賣自取下單，本人都未試過，下次可以試試，到時唔需要排隊，來到便可取走，現在還有信用卡優惠，更抵。

店內更有不少醬汁提供，當中是我們比較少接觸的。

下單需要走進店內最入的位置。

而廚房則在旁，地方雖小，五臓俱全。

他們以4款生牛肉湯河、海南雞飯、雞湯河、豬扒法包為主；再可自行配搭小食（春卷、雞翼、沙律、豬肉米紙卷等...

還有外賣自取的優惠$50便有去骨海南雞飯了。

越南去骨海南雞飯 - $50
望落比較簡單，雞煮得剛剛好熟，鮮嫩多汁，彈牙嫰滑，去了骨的雞連雞皮都超嫩有光澤，雞件去骨，食得放心，可大口大口地吃，而飯底加入了雞油更香更好味。

Decent food, comfy place.
Nice to have when you really miss Viet food.
Not the best value though.

位於灣仔大王東街28號小店，全店3人包辦。

食物不錯，有人情味添！

食物質素：⭐⭐⭐⭐
食物價格：⭐⭐⭐
服務質素：⭐⭐⭐⭐
環境舒適：⭐⭐⭐
整體而言：⭐⭐⭐⭐
Good value, genuine Vietnamese food done well.

As someone who’s spent time in Vietnam’s rural places - this place is both authentic and fantastic value. The Banh Mi is wonderfully on point (including the crunchy white baguette which is very rare in HK!); noodle salads are also great and fresh.
